---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Our Story | Victoria Herbs & Spices – Kenyan Heritage, Global Excellence"
  description="Discover the story behind Victoria Herbs & Spices: Three generations of farming wisdom, 500+ smallholder farmers, and a commitment to traceable, sustainable Kenyan herbs and spices."
>
  <!-- Hero Section - The Journey Begins -->
  <section
    class="relative h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
  >
    <!-- Background with Kenyan landscape -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516026672322-bc52d61a55d5?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80"
        alt="Kenyan highlands landscape"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-stone-900/90 via-stone-900/70 to-transparent"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 w-full">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <!-- Heritage Badge -->
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-amber-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-amber-300 text-sm mb-6 border border-amber-500/30"
        >
          <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
            <span
              class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-amber-400 opacity-75"
            ></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-amber-500"
            ></span>
          </span>
          🇰🇪 Nairobi, Kenya • Est. 2018
        </div>

        <h1
          class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display font-bold text-white leading-tight"
        >
          From Our Hands<br />to Your Table
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          A story of soil, sun, and generations of farming wisdom — bringing
          Kenya's finest herbs and spices to the world with integrity,
          traceability, and pride.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scroll Indicator -->
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center text-white/40 text-xs tracking-widest"
    >
      <span>OUR JOURNEY</span>
      <div
        class="w-px h-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-white/30 to-transparent mt-2"
      >
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline Navigation -->
  <div class="bg-white border-b border-stone-200 sticky top-20 z-40">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div
        class="flex overflow-x-auto hide-scrollbar gap-8 py-4 text-sm font-medium"
      >
        <a
          href="#beginnings"
          class="text-stone-600 hover:text-amber-600 transition whitespace-nowrap"
          >Our Beginnings</a
        >
        <a
          href="#philosophy"
          class="text-stone-600 hover:text-amber-600 transition whitespace-nowrap"
          >Our Philosophy</a
        >
        <a
          href="#farmers"
          class="text-stone-600 hover:text-amber-600 transition whitespace-nowrap"
          >Our Farmers</a
        >
        <a
          href="#journey"
          class="text-stone-600 hover:text-amber-600 transition whitespace-nowrap"
          >Farm to Export</a
        >
        <a
          href="#impact"
          class="text-stone-600 hover:text-amber-600 transition whitespace-nowrap"
          >Our Impact</a
        >
        <a
          href="#team"
          class="text-stone-600 hover:text-amber-600 transition whitespace-nowrap"
          >Our Team</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Our Beginnings -->
  <section id="beginnings" class="py-24 bg-white scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <span
            class="text-amber-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase"
            >Where It All Began</span
          >
          <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mt-4 text-stone-900 leading-tight"
          >
            A Vision Born<br />in the Highlands
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-6 mt-8 text-stone-700">
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
              In 2018, Victoria Wanjiku traveled from her family's farm in Meru
              to Nairobi with a simple mission: to find a better market for her
              community's moringa. What she discovered was a growing global
              demand for African herbs and spices — but a frustrating lack of
              trust, traceability, and fair pricing.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
              <span class="font-bold text-amber-600"
                >"Why should our farmers work so hard only to see others
                profit?"</span
              > she asked. That question became the foundation of Victoria Herbs
              & Spices — a company built on the belief that Kenyan farmers deserve
              recognition, fair compensation, and a direct connection to the global
              markets that value their craft.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
              Today, Victoria leads a team of 20 export specialists, working
              with over 500 smallholder farmers across five counties. But she
              still returns to Meru every month — to walk the fields, talk with
              farmers, and remember why this work matters.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Founder Quote -->
          <div
            class="mt-10 bg-amber-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-amber-500"
          >
            <p class="text-stone-700 italic text-lg">
              "Every moringa leaf, every chilli, every hibiscus flower carries
              the story of our farmers. When you choose Victoria, you're not
              just buying spices — you're investing in Kenyan families, Kenyan
              land, and Kenyan pride."
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-4">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl"
              >
                👩🏾
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-stone-900">Victoria Wanjiku</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-stone-500">
                  Founder & CEO • 3rd generation farmer
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1590779033100-9f60a05a013d?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=987&q=80"
            alt="Kenyan farmer in field"
            class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full h-80 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1527689368864-3a821dbccc34?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80"
              alt="Nairobi city skyline"
              class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full h-48 object-cover"
            />
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1615485290382-441e4d049cb5?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80"
              alt="Moringa harvest"
              class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full h-48 object-cover"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Philosophy -->
  <section id="philosophy" class="py-24 bg-stone-50 scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <span
          class="text-amber-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase"
          >What Guides Us</span
        >
        <h2
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mt-4 text-stone-900"
        >
          Our Core Beliefs
        </h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg mt-4">
          These four principles shape every decision we make, from farmer
          partnerships to export logistics.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition"
        >
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🌱</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">Traceability</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">
            Every batch can be traced back to the farmer who grew it. We believe
            transparency builds trust.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition"
        >
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🤝</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">
            Fair Partnership
          </h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">
            We pay above-market prices and provide training, seeds, and support
            to our farming partners.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition"
        >
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🌍</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">Sustainability</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">
            Rain-fed cultivation, no chemicals, and regenerative practices that
            protect the land for future generations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition"
        >
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">✨</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">Excellence</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">
            Only the finest herbs and spices meet our export standards — because
            our customers deserve nothing less.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Farmers -->
  <section id="farmers" class="py-24 bg-white scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <span
            class="text-amber-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase"
            >The Heart of Our Business</span
          >
          <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mt-4 text-stone-900"
          >
            Meet Our Farmers
          </h2>

          <p class="text-lg text-stone-700 mt-6 leading-relaxed">
            Behind every product is a farmer — someone who rises before dawn,
            who knows their land intimately, who takes pride in their craft. We
            work with over 500 smallholder farmers across five Kenyan counties,
            each bringing generations of agricultural wisdom.
          </p>

          <!-- Farmer Stats -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-10">
            <div class="bg-amber-50 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600">500+</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-stone-600">Partner Farmers</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-amber-50 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600">5</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-stone-600">Counties</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-amber-50 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600">70%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-stone-600">Women Farmers</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-amber-50 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600">3rd</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-stone-600">Generation Farmers</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Farmer Stories Carousel (simplified as cards) -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 to-stone-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-amber-200"
          >
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div
                class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl flex-shrink-0"
              >
                👩🏾‍🌾
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900">Grace Wanjiku</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-amber-600 mb-2">
                  Moringa farmer, Meru • 25 years
                </p>
                <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">
                  "Victoria pays fairly and on time. Now my children are in
                  better schools, and I've trained 15 other women in organic
                  farming practices."
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 to-stone-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-amber-200"
          >
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div
                class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl flex-shrink-0"
              >
                👨🏾‍🌾
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900">Joseph Mutua</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-amber-600 mb-2">
                  Chilli farmer, Machakos • 18 years
                </p>
                <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">
                  "The training on post-harvest handling doubled my income. Now
                  I'm teaching my sons the importance of quality over quantity."
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 to-stone-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-amber-200"
          >
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div
                class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl flex-shrink-0"
              >
                👩🏾
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900">Njoki Wambui</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-amber-600 mb-2">
                  Hibiscus farmer, Kiambu • 12 years
                </p>
                <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">
                  "We've been growing hibiscus for three generations. Victoria
                  helped us get organic certification — now our flowers go to
                  Europe!"
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Farm to Export Journey -->
  <section id="journey" class="py-24 bg-stone-50 scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <span
          class="text-amber-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase"
          >From Soil to Ship</span
        >
        <h2
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mt-4 text-stone-900"
        >
          The Journey of Your Spice
        </h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg mt-4">
          Traceability isn't just a buzzword — it's our promise. Here's how each
          product makes its way from Kenyan soil to your door.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Timeline Line (desktop) -->
        <div
          class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-amber-200 hidden lg:block"
        >
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-12">
          <!-- Step 1 -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:text-right">
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
                <span
                  class="inline-block bg-amber-600 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4"
                  >Step 1</span
                >
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">
                  Cultivation
                </h3>
                <p class="text-stone-600">
                  Farmers plant using traditional methods and organic practices.
                  No synthetic fertilizers or pesticides — just generations of
                  knowledge.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-amber-600 font-medium">
                  Counties: Meru, Machakos, Kiambu, Makueni, Kitui
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl z-10"
              >
                🌱
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 2 -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:order-2">
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
                <span
                  class="inline-block bg-amber-600 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4"
                  >Step 2</span
                >
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">
                  Harvesting
                </h3>
                <p class="text-stone-600">
                  Hand-picked at peak maturity. Our farmers know exactly when
                  each crop is ready — knowledge passed down through
                  generations.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-amber-600 font-medium">
                  Peak harvest: March-May & October-December
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:order-1 flex justify-center">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl z-10"
              >
                👐
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:text-right">
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
                <span
                  class="inline-block bg-amber-600 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4"
                  >Step 3</span
                >
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">
                  Sun Drying
                </h3>
                <p class="text-stone-600">
                  Traditional sun-drying on raised racks. No mechanical heat —
                  just the African sun, preserving natural oils and nutrients.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-amber-600 font-medium">
                  7-14 days depending on crop
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl z-10"
              >
                ☀️
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 4 -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:order-2">
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
                <span
                  class="inline-block bg-amber-600 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4"
                  >Step 4</span
                >
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">
                  Sorting & Grading
                </h3>
                <p class="text-stone-600">
                  Hand-sorted by our women's cooperative. Only the finest
                  quality makes it to export — the rest supports local markets.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-amber-600 font-medium">
                  Rejection rate: Under 15% (quality standard)
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:order-1 flex justify-center">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl z-10"
              >
                ✨
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 5 -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:text-right">
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
                <span
                  class="inline-block bg-amber-600 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4"
                  >Step 5</span
                >
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">
                  Lab Testing
                </h3>
                <p class="text-stone-600">
                  Every batch is tested by independent labs for purity, potency,
                  and safety. Certificates of Analysis accompany all shipments.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-amber-600 font-medium">
                  SGS Kenya • ISO 17025 accredited
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl z-10"
              >
                🔬
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 6 -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:order-2">
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
                <span
                  class="inline-block bg-amber-600 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4"
                  >Step 6</span
                >
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">
                  Packaging & Export
                </h3>
                <p class="text-stone-600">
                  Vacuum-sealed in food-grade packaging. Shipped from Mombasa
                  port to destinations worldwide with full documentation.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-amber-600 font-medium">
                  FOB Mombasa • Door-to-door logistics
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:order-1 flex justify-center">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl z-10"
              >
                ✈️
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Impact -->
  <section id="impact" class="py-24 bg-white scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <span
          class="text-amber-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase"
          >Making a Difference</span
        >
        <h2
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mt-4 text-stone-900"
        >
          Beyond Business
        </h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg mt-4">
          We measure success not just in containers shipped, but in lives
          improved and land preserved.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-stone-50 p-8 rounded-2xl text-center">
          <div class="text-6xl mb-4 text-amber-600">500+</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Farmers Empowered</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">
            Stable incomes, fair prices, and training in organic practices.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-50 p-8 rounded-2xl text-center">
          <div class="text-6xl mb-4 text-amber-600">70%</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Women-Led</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">
            The majority of our partner farmers and sorters are women.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-50 p-8 rounded-2xl text-center">
          <div class="text-6xl mb-4 text-amber-600">100%</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Chemical-Free</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">
            No synthetic pesticides or fertilizers on our partner farms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Community Projects -->
      <div class="mt-16 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-stone-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-amber-200"
        >
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4">
            Water Access Initiative
          </h3>
          <p class="text-stone-700 mb-4">
            Partnered with local communities to install 3 rainwater harvesting
            systems serving over 200 farming families.
          </p>
          <span class="text-sm text-amber-600">2024 • Meru County</span>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-stone-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-amber-200"
        >
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4">
            Women's Sorting Cooperative
          </h3>
          <p class="text-stone-700 mb-4">
